  "meta_title": "Horizon Pool at Keswick Hall | Luxury Resort in Charlottesville",
  "meta_description": "Overlook the Full Cry Golf Course from our 80-foot T-shaped swimming pool. Featuring infinity edges and a waterfall, Keswick Hall's Horizon Pool awaits. Book now.",
  "details_page_url": "horizon-pool",
  "short_description": "<p>Enjoy a vigorous lap in the early morning hours, order lunch in a poolside cabana or lounge at our T-shaped infinity edge as you take in the beauty of the mountain view.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>",
  "description": "<p>The Horizon Pool is a true focal point of the newly re-imagined Keswick Hall.</p>\n<p><br />Overlooking the lush Full Cry Golf Course with the beautiful mountains in the distance, our 80-foot T-shaped infinity-edge swimming pool is dual level with a 3-foot waterfall cascading over an 8-foot waterfall wall. Pool Terraces are thoughtfully designed to offer easy access to a variety of amenities including a refreshment bar, towel service, and changing rooms, all surrounded by gardens that provide a private and serene setting. The two pools will offer distinct heat settings on each level so that swimmers can choose their preference as well as built-in bench seating, wheelchair accessibility and a new ultra-violet light filtering system for clean chemical-free water.</p>\n<p><br />Special attention has been paid to the design of the in-pool and poolside lighting to create a dramatic evening ambiance, perfect to enjoy a refreshing cocktail as the day draws into night.</p>",
